---
title: Cal Smart Chunky Turkey Chilli with Pickled Jalapeños
description: A big bowl of chilli is a sure-fire way to get the whole family to eat their greens. Hiding in tonight's savoury chilli you'll find juicy chunks of turkey, tender squash and sweet peppers, all topped with pickled jalapeños!

